These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, grapefruit, eggplant, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, trance, jazz, country
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian, indonesian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, hedgehog, pony
 1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 2. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
 3. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 4. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 7. the malaysian is the person eating eggplant##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the pony and the fan of country##2
10. the person eating peach is the owner of the pony##1
11. the fan of jazz is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | eggplant  | peach    | strawberry    | grapefruit   |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | soul   | jazz       | country    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | nigerian | turkish    | indonesian |
| Pet           | frog | pony       | lizard | hedgehog     |

