.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, blueberry, artichoke, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, chess, card-games, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, egyptian, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, basketball, rowing, water-polo
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
 2. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person eating blueberry is the malaysian##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 6. the malaysian is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 7. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 8. the australian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 9. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating artichoke is in an odd position##4
11. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | pepper  | blueberry    | artichoke     | cherry       |
| Hobby         | card-games | sudoku | photography   | chess |
| Nationality   | egyptian | malaysian   | turkish   | australian    |
| Sport         | rowing | water-polo  | sailing | basketball   |

