.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, lemonade, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, journalist, dancer, lawyer
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, canadian, spanish, polish
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, frog, chinchilla
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
 2. the canadian is the dancer##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 4. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is the lawyer##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is the polish##1
 8. the lawyer is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the colombian##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | cola | lemonade   | 7up    | almond-milk      |
| Job           | dancer | freelancer | journalist | lawyer     |
| Nationality   | canadian      | polish   | colombian   | spanish |
| Pet           | chinchilla         | guinea-pig       | frog  | lizard       |

