.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, almond-milk, milk
There 4 different types of food: pear, pineapple, pomegranate, nectarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, camping, singing, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, skateboarding, soccer, basketball
 1. the person drinking coffee is the person eating pear##1
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 3. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is camping##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating nectarine##1
12. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk       | almond-milk   | coffee   | 7up   |
| Food       | pineapple        | nectarine | pear    | pomegranate       |
| Hobby      | skydiving | camping    | singing  | rock-climbing |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | soccer  | swimming | basketball    |

