.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lemon, broccoli, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, traveling, video-games, board-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, paramedic, electrician, teacher
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo, golf, parkour
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person eating plum##2
 3. the electrician is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the paramedic is the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the security-guard is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating lemon is the security-guard##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is the paramedic##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
10. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | broccoli    | plum      | eggplant          | lemon    |
| Hobby   | traveling | board-games       | video-games | photography |
| Job     | teacher     | electrician      | paramedic     | security-guard |
| Sport   | water-polo   | parkour | golf        | skateboarding   |

