There 4 different types of food: zucchini, eggplant, kale, kiwi
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, country, rock, electronic
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine, french, turkish
 1. the person eating kale is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 3. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of electronic is between the french and the fan of country##2
 7. the fan of rock is the person eating kale##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is the person eating kale##1
 9. the argentine is on the far right##1
10. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | juice  | sprite    | almond-milk       | milk       |
| Food          | kiwi    | kale | eggplant | zucchini     |
| Music-Genre   | disco | rock        | electronic    | country   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | french      | turkish    | argentine |

