 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
10. the british is on the far right##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
12. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
