4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goldfish, chinchilla, hamster
 1. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 3. the german is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the chinese is on the right of the malaysian##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the dutch##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is between the german and the person watching satire movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
12. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

