.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, tea, fanta
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, cooking, skydiving, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, scientific, superhero, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, lacrosse, snowboarding, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea       | lemonade | cola        | fanta        |
| Hobby         | baking | skydiving       | traveling | cooking |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | scientific        | drama    | superhero      |
| Sport         | lacrosse     | snowboarding    | baseball | rugby   |

