.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, hip-hop, folk, disco
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, malaysian, egyptian, colombian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, golf, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, roller, airplane, van
 1. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is golf##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is between the argentine and the colombian##2
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the malaysian##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 8. the colombian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
10. the argentine is in an even position##4
11. the argentine is on the far right##1
12. the fan of classical is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | classical | disco     | folk        |
| Nationality   | egyptian | colombian  | malaysian     | argentine |
| Sport         | cricket    | surfing | golf      | snowboarding |
| Transport     | van | roller     | airplane | ship       |

 